high_descs: walk to face right sink cabinet
take out toilet roll from bottom right cabinet
move left to face counter between sinks
put toilet roll on counter
walk to face toilet paper hanger
pick up toilet paper from toilet paper hanger
walk to face counter between sinks
put toilet paper on counter
anns.task_desc: put toilet roll and paper on bathroom counter

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the wall, then turn left to face the counter.
Open the rightmost cabinet door below the counter and take out the toilet paper tube, then close the cabinet.
Turn left and walk forward, then turn right to face the counter.
Put the cardboard toilet paper tube on the counter in between the two sinks.
Turn right and walk over to the wall.
Pick up the toilet paper roll off of the toilet paper holder.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn right and walk up to the counter.
Put the toilet paper roll on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Move two toilet paper rolls to the counter.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the far sink, facing it.
Take the toilet paper roll out of the bottom right cabinet.
Take a step left.
Place the toilet paper roll on between the sinks, to the left of the spray bottle
Turn around and face the toilet.
Take the toilet paper roll off the toilet paper holder.
Turn left and walk to the center of the sinks.
Place the toilet paper roll on the counter behind the space between the other toilet paper roll and the spray bottle.
anns.task_desc: Place two toilet paper rolls on a counter.
